AUDIO: 'In less than 7 minutes, I built this entire multi-platform marketing campaign from absolute scratch, complete with a premium logo, print-ready menus, custom packaging mock-ups, and high-end video ads. No Photoshop, no complex design'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'tools, and no expensive agency. Today, I\'m showing you exactly how to do this for your own business using Lovart AI. All right, when you first log into Lovart, you will be greeted by this clean interface where the main engine is'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'this prompt box right in the center. On the left side of the box, there\'s a plus sign where you can upload reference files or turn on web search. Right next to that is a book-shaped icon. Clicking this opens the skills section, which is'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'a lot like using specific skill in Claude code. There are finely-tuned skills for social media, e-commerce, branding, et cetera. You\'ll also see a lightbulb icon that lets you toggle the thinking mode on and off. Next to that'

